eZ GPG extension configuration (tutorial)
=================================================

A few users of eZ GPG may require further
documentation extension of the default eZ publish store features.

If you are interested in sponsoring the development
of any of these features for your eZ publish web site,
please contact info@brookinsconsulting.com

=================================================
#0 - Install GPG



=================================================
#1 - Configure GPG Keyring

Install existing key or create new key in gpg settings directory, extension/ezpg/settings/.gpg

Example howto, http://nmlug.org/faqs/gen-gpg-key.html

> If you do not install a valid key, you may get an error message like this ...

Error: 
validate_key: /usr/bin/gpg --no-secmem-warning --homedir /web/pro/example_com/doc/extension/ezpg/settings/.gpg --list-keys admin@example.com


=================================================
#2 - Configure eZ GPG settings

   extension/ezpg/settings/ezpg.ini


=================================================
#3 - Use eZ GPG Functions or Template Operators in your eZ publish installation


